summary: This is a small tweak of the two mods owned by Skvindt and AlphaJoe they have all rights to these mods. all I did is downloaded theirs and moved the building around a bit of landscaping as well so that they are compatible with each other.
descriptionHtml: This is a small tweak of the two mods owned by Skvindt and AlphaJoe they have all rights to these mods. all I did is downloaded theirs and moved the building around a bit of landscaping as well so that they are compatible with each other. make sure to load it with windstad Mine first otherwise you will see bad meshing of the land. I am not a modder so it's not perfect but it is good to see my two favorite mods working together. the modders are more than welcome to download this tweak fix and re-upload if they please I can't wait to see their new stuff.
author: Skvindt and AlphaJoe  andrewblough81
